{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"0aef95ba00","title":"右派言论——攻击党报","origin":"《社会主义辩论集之二  毒草集(资产阶级右派的反社会主义言论)》，湖南人民出版社1957年10月版，内部发行。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"371bfd39ae","index":0,"year":1957,"month":6,"day":null,"articleId":"0aef95ba00"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"32c4df5349","name":"孙天霖"},{"id":"88d91c371f","name":"陆铿"},{"id":"9b57a01b04","name":"云南"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"47bf2cb442","type":"title","text":"右派言论——攻击党报","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0aef95ba00"},{"id":"a797d4270b","type":"authors","text":"云南陆铿孙天霖","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0aef95ba00"},{"id":"6fa76f9f27","type":"paragraph","text":"陆铿(云南省政协委员)","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0aef95ba00"},{"id":"512ce00864","type":"paragraph","text":"问题是决定编辑方针，掌握编辑方针的人，倒不一定有对读者负责的愿望。他们考虑的可能主要是“领导意图”，读者爱看固好，不爱看活该，反正领导不啃声就行了。报纸究竟是办成教科书、布告牌，还是变成人人所乐于享用的精神粮，这是上面决定的，编辑、记者只能照书执行。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0aef95ba00"},{"id":"c151254d9b","type":"paragraph","text":"现在只有一家大型铅印日报，在外国人看来，民主空气就很难说。办一家民间报纸和云南日报唱对台戏也未尝不可，对“百花齐放、百家争鸣”也有好处。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0aef95ba00"},{"id":"34a584b82b","type":"paragraph","text":"孙天霖(云南省工商联副主委)","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0aef95ba00"},{"id":"872c7905f1","type":"paragraph","text":"……我要问一问：云南日报是否在我们工商界的阶级关系中，愿意制造和挑拨矛盾？这非常重要，决不是说“气话”。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0aef95ba00"}],"page":{"id":"7685ca76d5","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0aef95ba00","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}